text: Miguel Ángel Navarro Quintero (born 11 January 1951) is a Mexican physician and politician. He is a member of the National Regeneration Movement (Morena). He was elected Governor of Nayarit in 2021. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican politicians Category:People from Nayarit
title: Miguel Ángel Navarro Quintero
